### 7. Language Selector
Add language toggle button to header right section:
- Position: right side of header, before wallet button
- Labels: "EN" / "中文" (toggle)
- Default: "EN"
- State: stored in localStorage key "ion-dex-lang"
- Visual: pill-shaped button, 36px height, text-sm font-bold
