## Implementation Order
1. Fix theme.css border-radius values
2. Reduce glass opacity from 0.35→0.22
3. Boost neon glow values (per table above)
4. Reduce blur 24px→16px, saturate 1.3→1.6
5. Add home navigation (AppShell.tsx)
6. Add language selector (AppShell.tsx)
7. Verify all pages render correctly
8. Run: node skills/ion-dex-commander/scripts/git-auto-deploy.mjs

## Anti-Patterns (NEVER)
- border-radius < 1rem on any visible element
- backdrop-filter: none on cards
- bg alpha > 0.30 on glass cards
- text color darker than #c0d8f0
- hardcoded language strings (use i18n)
- missing home navigation on any page
